Movie/Show Synopsis: A middle-aged man, Tim McVey, attempts to reclaim his 1984 world record on Nibbler, the first billion-point video game.
Movie/Show Sales Pitch: Man vs Snake is a hilarious and heartfelt documentary about obsession, legacy, and endurance in the world of classic arcade gaming. A multi-award winner for Best Documentary and Editing, its hailed as one of the best gaming docs ever and is shown in university film courses worldwide.
